    <div class="short_content_box">
        <div class="short_content">
    </p>
    <p>He was the first African to be hired by Google in 2007.
        Prior to joining Google, he worked for Wananchi On-line, a company he co-founded in 1999 both as CEO and
        Strategy and Business Development Director. In December 2010, he was awarded the honor of Moran of the Burning
        Spear (MBS) by H.E. Hon. Uhuru Kenyatta, President of Kenya, for his outstanding contribution towards
        technology.
        He attended the Stanford Executive Program of Stanford University Graduate School of Business in 2008. He holds
        a BSc. (Joint Hons) in Economics &amp; Computer Science from City University London. Secretary Mucheru has been
        a Director of several renowned Companies in Kenya.</p>

