    relationships. Shaun is currently working with a cross-agency team on generating agro-enterprise content for
    cloud-based distance learning systems and creating farmer-facing business tools using ICT solutions. Shaun holds a
    Bachelor’s in Horticultural Science from Reading University, a Master’s in Tropical Agriculture from Nottingham
    University and a PhD in Plant Physiology from Cranfield University.</p>
