        A. Simiyu, Executive Director, Good Neighbors Community Development Initiative (GNCDI)</strong></p>
<p>Zebby Simiyu is involved in empowering both small-scale farmers, individuals, and institutions with appropriate
    skills and knowledge in producing and marketing high quality horticultural produce. She works directly with farmer
    groups promoting horticultural products and marketing the same through the Good Neighbors Enterprises.</p>
