        President for Policy and Campaigns, Oxfam
        America</strong></p>
<p>Dr. Paul O&#8217;Brien is the Vice President for Policy and Campaigns at Oxfam America where he oversees research,
    policy, advocacy, and campaigning work to influence the US government and US corporations.</p>
<p>
<div class="short_content_box">
